          "type": "text",
          "text": "Abstract",
          "position": [36.0, 160.0, 100.0, 175.0],
          "sub_type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "layout_id": 4,
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This paper presents a comprehensive overview of deep learning techniques applied to natural language processing tasks. We review transformer-based architectures and their applications in machine translation, sentiment analysis, and text classification.",
          "position": [36.0, 180.0, 540.0, 250.0],
          "sub_type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "layout_id": 5,
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Introduction",
          "position": [36.0, 280.0, 180.0, 295.0],
          "sub_type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "layout_id": 6,
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Natural language processing (NLP) has undergone significant transformation with the advent of deep learning. Recent advances in neural architectures have led to unprecedented performance improvements across diverse NLP tasks.",
